{"tid":1881615,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國參議員提「台灣主權象徵法案」 促讓台灣官員訪美可秀國旗","createTime":"2020-02-15T16:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T08:47:29.000Z","uid":70063,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1a70721abe5b933b49806ac8295c53c2981174d1","tid":1881615,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:16:31.000Z","msg":"美國參議員克魯茲今天推出最新法案，盼鬆綁台灣人員在美所受限制。法案表示，美方應准許執行公務的台灣外交、軍方人員，在美國領土展示國旗、穿著制服。<br />\n<br />\n美國共和黨籍參議員克魯茲（Ted Cruz）今天所推出的法案名為「台灣主權象徵法案」（Taiwan Symbols of Sovereignty Act，簡稱Taiwan SOS Act），旨在鬆綁美方對「台灣主權象徵」的禁令。<br />\n<br />\n法案也獲得其他8位共和黨籍參議員連署，包含盧比歐（Marco Rubio）、柯頓（Tom Cotton）、霍利（Josh Hawley）、楊恩（Todd Young）、史考特（Rick Scott）、柯寧（John Cornyn）、薩斯（Ben Sasse）及布萊克本（Marsha Blackburn）。<br />\n<br />\n克魯茲在新聞稿中表示，希望透過法案，推翻美國前總統歐巴馬（Barack Obama）政府在中共要求下，於2015年所頒布禁止台灣展示國旗的機密備忘錄。備忘錄也使得美國國務院及國防部，無法在社群網站上張貼台灣主權象徵圖樣，限制美國對台支持。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士先前告訴中央社記者，這一備忘錄被稱為「對台交往準則」（Guidelines on the Relationship with Taiwan），源於2015年1月台灣駐美代表處在雙橡園的爭議升旗事件。駐美代表處當時在雙橡園舉行元旦升旗典禮，是睽違36年後中華民國國旗首次在華府飄揚，引發美方強烈不滿。<br />\n<br />\n克魯茲指出，美國不應聽命於中共，強迫來自自由、民主政府的軍方及外交人員，將國旗隱藏起來或丟棄他們的制服。<br />\n<br />\n克魯茲說：「中國對台灣、美國區域好友惡意日益增加，美方及世界其他國家須堅定與台灣站在一起，這是十分重要的。允許台灣官員能在美國驕傲展示他們的國旗，就是正確的第一步。」<br />\n<br />\n長期友台的盧比歐也表示，當北京在國際上加倍孤立台灣之際，這一法案將能進一步增強美台關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3067636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3067636&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFx8vW%2Fvk9QtnWk1JKGKfj%2Fbg%3D&h=a43a3c15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3067636&h=f5ec77a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3067636</a>"},{"pid":"d200e580ed6c48c8b24d4671b94ae64c1acf158a","tid":1881615,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:17:53.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFx8vW%2Fvk9QtnWk1JKGKfj%2Fbg%3D&h=44dd0ce8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"3acee18f91d197c651677eaa29b7072152907a5c","tid":1881615,"uid":200200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:19:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6055c389f1bf34fbbf5863bd0beebd1a482b819c","tid":1881615,"uid":58552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:19:42.000Z","msg":"共和黨 兩大中生代明星<br />\nTed <br />\nRubio"},{"pid":"e90a537d033137c7832711c66b12518918811de0","tid":1881615,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:19:54.000Z","msg":"小英有美國保佑，又有港共同中共助攻，真係行運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842af4c8975bf83e24f98f98246741f58e6b8049","tid":1881615,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cd9deef647be9dec47e7f7d6ab4b4c6589fd2ac","tid":1881615,"uid":265839,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:32:36.000Z","msg":"美國前總統歐巴馬（Barack Obama）政府在中共要求下，於2015年所頒布禁止台灣展示國旗的機密備忘錄<br />\n<br />\n力架馬奶共狗"},{"pid":"953a00f0a3d9d98dc7ffb1ed57f0e4ceb5db563e","tid":1881615,"uid":42662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:33:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d56b77fa053edc8046dfc512d9